Snow_dtt_dogers

You need to ride over 9 levels with you're snow-board ! You can unlock a new snow-board when you pass 3 new levels !

Tips : Put a BOT in CT to prevent the round to restart . Type cl_ragdoll_physics_enable 0 in the console when you play this map or when you connecting a server with this map ! This map may not run on some servers ...

http://teamdtt.o-n.fr

Enjoy !
